snippet.title: Cut the Rope: Magic Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Out Dec 17 for iOS, Android and Amazon!

Brand new chapter in the award-winning Cut the Rope puzzle series is coming this December!

In Cut the Rope: Magic, Om Nom accidentally teleports into an enchanted book, chasing an evil wizard who has stolen all of his candies. But little monster's got his own tricks this time - like the power of shapeshifting!

Find out more about Cut the Rope: Magic:
- Visit Magic's official website: https://magic.cuttherope.net
- Like us Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/cuttherope
- Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Cut_The_Rope
